S|# Novizio — Rules & Never-Again Patterns|> LONG-TERM. Novizio-specific only. System-wide rules → docs/mem/feedback.md // > Schema: each rule must have [added: YYYY-MM-DD] · Rules without dates are invalid. // > Append-only. Never delete. Update wording in-place if a rule evolves. // > 🔴 CRITICAL — always loaded · 🟡 IMPORTANT — load if task touches this domain · 🟢 GUIDANCE — on demand // ---
S|🔴 CRITICAL|- [added: 2026-03-26] Never use: "sale", "hurry", "limited time", "affordable", "cheap", "budget" — kills premium positioning permanently // - [added: 2026-03-26] Captions: one idea per sentence. No run-ons. 1–2 sentences max. No exclamation points. // - [added: 2026-04-30] Copy tone must never sound: mass-market, fast-fashion, salesy, or desperate // ---
S|🟡 IMPORTANT|- [added: 2026-04-30] Atlas: muted tones, natural light only. No busy backgrounds. Think editorial magazine spread. // - [added: 2026-04-30] Rio: Meta + Instagram ads only. Explicitly exclude bargain-hunter and discount-seeker interest segments. // - [added: 2026-04-15] Kai: IG ER drop > 20% WoW = flag immediately to Marcus — do not wait for weekly rv // ---
S|🟢 GUIDANCE|- [added: 2026-03-26] Instagram primary CTA: "Shop the drop →" · Secondary: "Explore the collection" // - [added: 2026-04-15] cnt format: Reels for reach, carousels for saves — confirmed by Kai performance data // - [added: 2026-03-26] Hashtags: niche fashion + aesthetic tags only. Never mass tags (#fashion, #style, #ootd) // ---
S|Never Again|> Errors that occurred and must not repeat. Format: [date] — what went wrong — rule. // _No entries yet. Populated from Adjourning after any Novizio error._